Honestly, 
I was only interested in this game, because it's the same publisher as Stardew Valley. I was excited bc of the pixel graphics.
But I've come to really love the game, and here are my reasons:
1. Pixel Graphics;
2. Story-Rich;
3. Good mix of exploration-story-combat and boss battles;
4. Has mini-games inside the game (like a whole little story game);
5. The insane controller compatibility;
6. Runs well on MacOS, never had problems with it.
Great game, I highly recommend. Esp. for people who get freaked out by combat, fpf games
